{"product_id": "201870", "page": 9, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-22", "text": "Download this:\nIt's the better version of Uplay, which Ubisoft regularly updates, tweeks, and fixes, before you buy AC:Revelations. Because Steam give you a version of Ye Olde! Uplay, which will eventually give you a bad time.\nGoogle Authenicator (for iphones and androids)/Windows Authenicator (for Windows Phones/Nokia) - To prevent more infamous pirates from stealing your account in the first place.\nLast Pass - So you won't lose the password to your Ubisoft account (and more important things) ever again.\nMake a separate e-mail account just for gaming, mainly G-Mail and/or any strong and unhackable e-mail severs. Because Yahoo! is hacker bait.\nIf someone steals your account and enables 2-Step Verification, go log into your\naccount and send in your support ticket. There's a working customer support, unlike in the dark first Uplay's days, so contact them.\nIf that doesn't work, there's other methods to get help.\n\n\nand\n(Full Game review coming soon).\nToo busy getting slaughter by the other players. Trying to \"Git Gud.\"", "hours": 0.7, "user_id": "76561198031855571", "username": "pachirisuGrrl33", "products": 22, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
