{"product_id": "201870", "page": 12, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-10-09", "text": "Cons:\n-Repetitive\n-Stupid AI; Ubisoft seems like they're making progress though.\n-Boring Story\n-Some areas are made more annoying than challenging.  Completing them seems more like a chore and it\u2019s to very fulfilling.\n-Hideout seemed almost useless, I only went there when I was forced to by a quest.\n-Buying the stores and landmarks was kind of interesting in Brotherhood but it became very repetitive. It\u2019s recycled in this game.\nPros\n-Graphics\n-Fun combat\n-Some fun scenes that almost seem like a movie cinematic but you\u2019re controlling the characters.\n-Awesome Soundtrack and songs play at the right moments.\n-Some Interesting Characters\n-Story is completed with a nice ending for Alta\u00efr and Ezio", "hours": 16.3, "user_id": "76561197981045627", "username": "qnff8k", "products": 182, "early_access": false}
