{"product_id": "201870", "page": 12, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-10-07", "text": "I love the Assassin's Creed games dearly. The graphics, the atmosphre created in-game, I find the story intriguing and the character absolutely well written. Another thing that works for me is that the game is not so hard, as to take away the desire of moving forward in the story,  but neither is it too easy - it still offers up a challenge here and there. I am very much looking forward to discovering the later games once this one is done! Yes, keyboard controls aren't ideal, but you can do just fine without a controller (and I am not the best of gamers but any means).", "hours": 24.4, "user_id": "76561198212087267", "username": "Valkyrie90", "products": 87, "early_access": false}
