{"product_id": "201870", "page": 22, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-06-27", "text": "Even though I enjoy playing AC and even more playing with Ezio, this game gets a little stale for me and I cannot find the motivation for getting through the game.\nThe missions is kinda repetitive and the bomb craftings is really boring and I have almost never used them.\nAnd don't even get me started on the defence of the dens :/\nBuuuuuut... it is great that it connects the memories of Altair and Ezio and some day I may find the interest to complete the game. And the improvement of the battles is as always great and makes it more enjoyable.", "hours": 7.0, "user_id": "76561198139903364", "username": "taz96", "products": 202, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
