{"product_id": "201870", "page": 25, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-05-20", "text": "Unplayable!  This game is so bugged I can't even play it.  It gliches out like crazy.  I've had the game for a while.  Unfortunately, when I first bought the game and tried it then, it was working fine. I logged about 3-4 hours of gameplay and then haven;t returned to play it until now.   I'm not sure what has changed or why it is very buggy. I doubt I can get a refund or a new game key from steam since I am over the time limits etc.  It's a shame because I was trying to get through all of the Creed games in chronological order and am afraid I might have to skip this one.  I would rather not have to buy a new one, but I guess $20 isn't too bad to pay for it on amazon.", "hours": 46.8, "user_id": "76561198023085811", "username": "Sentinal", "products": 81, "early_access": false}
