{"product_id": "201870", "page": 29, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-03-11", "text": "Assassin's Creed Revelations is, in my opinion, the best AC game of all time, the gameplay is extremely fun, and most importantly, you get the high jump back while climbing, one of my biggest problems with Brotherhood was that the high jump, something learned in 2, was removed,\nBut was reintroduced into Revelations along with the extraordinary hookblade, another thing, ziplines, I absolutely loved using them, especially the zip line Assassination. When I finished the game I was extremely disappointed that it was over, I'll defenatly be replaying Revelations, as soon as I finish AC 1 and 3!", "hours": 17.2, "user_id": "76561198291363285", "username": "Ori", "products": 41, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "201870", "page": 29, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-03-11", "text": "Heeelllo to everyone.\nWe're with one of the AC game which has perfect graphics for the date of this game.\nIf you have a question about Is it worthing for paying, yeah. Answer is yes.\nI lost a lot of time in Revelations. I was playing it in internet cafe. But after i found it in black friday, i didn't miss the chance to get it. You can see a lot of Greek&Turkish action in Constantinople. And if you're in with Ottomans or Byzantines, you're welcome !\nHerkese merhabalar.\nTarihine g\u00f6re m\u00fckemmel grafikleri olan bir AC oyunu ile beraberiz.\nE\u011fer kafan\u0131zda \u00f6demeye de\u011fer mi gibi sorular var ise, cevap evet.\n\u00c7ok fazla s\u00fcre harcad\u0131m Revelations'un i\u00e7inde. \u0130nternet kafede oynuyordum ama kara cumada indirimdeyken buldu\u011fumda alma f\u0131rsat\u0131n\u0131 ka\u00e7\u0131rmad\u0131m.\nOyunun i\u00e7inde a\u015f\u0131r\u0131 derecede Yunan&T\u00fcrk aksiyonlar\u0131 hareketlerini Konstantiniyye'de g\u00f6rebilirsiniz.\nVe Osmanl\u0131larla ya da Bizansl\u0131larla i\u00e7li d\u0131\u015fl\u0131ysan\u0131z, ho\u015fgeldiniz.", "hours": 65.1, "username": "\u2720Luftwaffe'sJackSparrow|ALI|", "products": 121, "early_access": false}
