{"product_id": "201870", "page": 30, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-02-28", "text": "Out of the Assassin's Creed games I've played so far (2, Brotherhood & Revelations), this one was probably my favorite.\nI especially found the \"mini games\" and side quests slightly more interesting than in the previous ones, though they are probably still not one of ACs greatest assets.\nConstantinople is absolutely beautiful and the story remains interesting. If you liked the previous AC games, you'll like this one as well.", "hours": 18.0, "username": "Exterminans27", "products": 291, "early_access": false}
