{"product_id": "201870", "page": 32, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-01-16", "text": "A definite improvement over brotherhood\nPROS:\n- A great wrap up of Ezio's story\n- THE HOOKBLADE\n- The combat is great, as usual\n- Impressive graphics\n- Great setting\n- Interesting characters\nCONS:\n- Den defense, like wtf\n- Uplay\nA solid wrap up of Altair and Ezio. A solid 8/10 game", "hours": 38.5, "username": "\u00d8rjan", "products": 176, "early_access": false}
