{"product_id": "201870", "page": 34, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-01-01", "text": "**** (of 5) Very good Athmosphere and story of the game. As the story unfolds you get used to controls and environment. The improvement of street battles is a good bonus, but otherwise the game mechanics are similar to its predecessor. I like the end again and hope the story will continue to stay mysterious.", "hours": 31.0, "user_id": "76561198065545417", "username": "Ralf the Huge", "products": 320, "early_access": false}
