{"product_id": "201870", "page": 37, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-27", "text": "Dear Claudia,\nThis game's storyline is amazing. It details the final missions of your brother, Ezio Auditore da Firenze, while introducing a bunch of different and memorable characters and locations for you to explore.\nIt also explores the memories of Altair Ibn-La'ahad, one of the greatest mentors that shaped the way the Creed is today. It picked up where his story left off, in the first game in the series, and gave a satisfying yet saddening ending.\nAlthough the game sometimes makes me jump off a wall when I don't want to, I still love this game.\nTruely yours,\nDaemonic", "hours": 23.2, "username": "Daemonic", "products": 49, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
