{"product_id": "201870", "page": 44, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-10-05", "text": "Very amazing experience. I recommend every single Assassins creed game on the market. Each one gives you a similar, yet, completely different, wonderful experience.\nAC revelations runs smoothly on lower end PC's, even running at about 30 FPS, lowest settings, on some laptops.\nI've played for 79 hours on this game, and still havent beaten it. There's so much to explore, and so much to do.", "hours": 82.8, "username": "blvckmage", "products": 79, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
