{"product_id": "201870", "page": 45, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-09", "text": "While I have some mixed feelings about the game, It's a kind of a closure to the Ezio trilogy.\nIn terms of gameplay, rip-off with minor changes.\nIn terms of plotline, the game had an unexpected plotline, for the good and for the bad.\nIn terms of Graphics, the game is colourful (in contrast to previous games, and even following games)", "hours": 31.3, "username": "The most Glorious one", "products": 239, "early_access": false}
