{"product_id": "201870", "page": 46, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-06", "text": "If you ever thought that your Ezio was overpowered before, get a load of Assassin's Creed Revelations. Now he has different kinds of\nbombs - to add to your arsenal of of hidden blades, poison darts, swords, guns, anything you might want. Oh, and a \"hook-blade\" to give you even more mobility.\nStory is the same Assassin's Creed jazz - if you liked it before, you'll like it still. Istambul is nice city to explore, you can have fun with that.", "hours": 19.9, "user_id": "76561198020205810", "username": "Delevion", "products": 160, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "201870", "page": 46, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-06", "text": "It's another Assasins Creed game, this time, something.", "hours": 3.5, "user_id": "76561197970701643", "username": "Liam Neeson Punching Wolves", "products": 1160, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "201870", "page": 46, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-02", "text": "More AC....yay!  The problem is that it's just that....more AC.  I love the franchise.  I love parkouring  my way up buildings that should be unscalable...I love droppimg down on enemies and cutting their throats...I love everything about the franchise...\nEXCEPT the hard fact that it hasn't progressed at all from the initial jump from AC1 to AC2.  Now, I'm a firm believer in the notion that \"if it ain't broke, don't fix it\".  Assassin's Creed has always been about climbing, jumping, leaping over obstacles that no mortal man could handle, and that's why I keep playing.  And I will keep on playing thru AC3 and all subsequent releases.  BUT the devs have GOT to add something else to the mix to keep it interesting.\nBottom line...if you liked AC2, and Brotherhood, you'll enjoy this release.  I liked it simply because it's more of the same AC that I love.  But don't expect anything revolutionary here...it's what you crave, but nothing more.", "hours": 188.0, "user_id": "76561197976515781", "username": "fishhooks", "products": 529, "early_access": false}
