{"product_id": "201870", "page": 50, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-07-04", "text": "An early Assassin's Creed part but still a good one. It has way less collectibles and side mission content as other titles but the ones that are in the game are good choosen. The main story is a bit short and I completed it in 22 hours. You have not to much money to spend and always you can buy something usefull. The controlls are a bit weird if you started with earlier games in the series as me but it was no big thing for me.\nBuy it in a Sale and you will be happy with it.", "hours": 24.7, "username": "SuperSandro2000", "products": 902, "early_access": false}
