{"product_id": "201870", "page": 51, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-26", "text": "AC Revelations is an excellent game, the new mechanics it introduced are easy to understand and to use, adding more versatility in fighting and assassinating enemies.\nEzio's story is the one you want, and also the one you need.\nI'd recommend exploring the optional content for more fun, such as the new set of unbreakable armor, master assassin quests, hideout sieges, etc.\nWord of Advice: Don't worry about bomb materials, they are plentiful and you'll get to restock very often.", "hours": 21.2, "username": "FireIceBlade", "products": 90, "early_access": false}
