{"product_id": "201870", "page": 68, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-12-24", "text": "Ending the Ezio games in Istanbul (or whatever name you want to use for it) I thought it interesting to change the whole setting from Italian to Turkish (or Ottoman).\nTruly, seeing Ezio grow from an impatient young man to a wise and slightly more patient older man is a very nice progress.\nI must say, tough, Roger Craig (voice actor of Ezio) is one of the few people I've heard doing a good older version of his character. Most people don't really seem able to pull it off properly.", "hours": 81.7, "username": "Seerk", "products": 263, "early_access": false}
