{"product_id": "201870", "page": 74, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-31", "text": "A great end to the story of Ezio Auditore. Revelations continues to work on the ideas of Brotherhood, but makes some welcome introductions, such as the bombs, the hook-blade and the Mediterranean War. Besides, this game is tied strongly to the first Assassin's Creed game and Altair's story.\nAll in all, one of the best games in the series.", "hours": 47.4, "username": "Nocturnal Stalker", "products": 761, "early_access": false}
