{"product_id": "201870", "page": 81, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-08-12", "text": "Assassin's Creed Revelations brings us the final chapter of Ezio's story, and takes us to the magnificent city of Constantinople or Istanbul. There are several new weapons along with many memorable moments along the way that truly defines Ezio's final chapter.\nPros:\n-Hookblade (combat and navigation)\n-Old Ezio\n-Story\n-Graphics\n-Environment and Scenery\n-Bomb Crafting\n-Altair Missions\nCons:\n-Uplay\n-Some ridiculous bugs\n-Doesn't really concludes Ezio life after retiring from Assassins\n-Limited present day interactions\n9/10", "hours": 27.0, "username": "Adrielputra58", "products": 107, "early_access": false}
