{"product_id": "201870", "page": 86, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-27", "text": "Final chapter of Ezio adventures and one the best AC game !\nAwesome story, great fighting, good graphics, and cool weapons. Its a great AC game! Has everything you want out of Assassins Creed. Bomberman Ezio !!! because no one game has a such deep expierence with mixing all kinds of bombs !! Cherry bomb !!\nNow to the other AC games !\n8/10", "hours": 23.4, "username": "L3Gi0n4R", "products": 411, "early_access": false}
