{"product_id": "201870", "page": 87, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-23", "text": "whether you are playing this game for ezio's story conclusion or just for the gameplay . you won't be disappointed .\nthe story is 10/10 .\nwe followed ezio from birth to death and shared so many memories with him it feels as if he existed in reality\nthe gameplay is 8/10 .\nnothing particularly noticable about the fighting system it has improved a bit from brotherhood and assassin's creed 2 . the hook blade brought a certain unique aspect to the gameplay , defending dins and sending your recruits on missions was a nice side game to have . however crafting bombs and all the complications that come with them was not something i liked . just my personal opinion . a simple smoke bomb would have done it .", "hours": 17.8, "username": "Blaze", "products": 28, "early_access": false}
