{"product_id": "201870", "page": 88, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-06-20", "text": "Absolutely terrible experience. I wish I could rate this game based off of its content. However, seemingly irrelevant programs have rendered me unable to start and actually play the game.\nAfter downloading the game itself, I have to download some \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ttass program called Uplay so that these \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665s can track my progress for some dumbass reason. But guess what - uplay never works and always crashes everytime i try to open it. Therefore, the game never turns on and I am never able to play it.\nI'm rating this right now without even playing the game , because GAME OWNERS SHOULD BE ABLE TO PLAY THEIR \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ING GAMES WITHOUT ANY \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ING STUPIDASS PROBLEMS. Get your\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665together ubisoft.", "hours": 3.0, "username": "EasyMoney", "products": 4, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
