{"product_id": "201870", "page": 101, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-31", "text": "10/10 would stab dirty Templars again\nMAJOR SPOILER:\nIf you beat all 5 Desmond sequences you can play AS Desmond! That's so cool! I mean I know its just a skin redo but seriously I love it, and I love the writing of Desmond's backstory.", "hours": 25.9, "username": "Chef Boi R D", "products": 81, "early_access": false}
