{"product_id": "201870", "page": 106, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-14", "text": "Worth it, if you can get it working. It was a big hastle to get this game to finally work, but once I did, it is pretty good. I had to uninstall the uplay stuff that was downloaded, restart my computer, download uplay from their website, restart again, then I was finally able to login, exit uplay and go back on and enter the key to play the game. I wish Ubisoft wouldnt use 3rd party systems because they are just a waste of time. So far, great game, would buy if it's on sale.", "hours": 16.3, "username": "shay4545", "products": 44, "early_access": false}
