{"product_id": "201870", "page": 114, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-30", "text": "They improved the keyboard controls. The chosen country is less enchanting than Italy, but the storyline counterbalance well enough.They wonderfully threaded the stories of Desmond and Ezio. I've played twice because it's so good. You need to play this game before playing AC3, to my opinion.", "hours": 66.9, "user_id": "76561198001584035", "username": "BobMammoth", "products": 314, "early_access": false}
