{"product_id": "201870", "page": 123, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-06", "text": "Discovering the life of our mentore, Altair - Ezio is getting through everything, that stands in his way. One of the best Assassin's Creed titles our there. If you get into the story, you will feel really well. After first playthrough, when finding Altair in his library, I felt chill going down my spine. It felt great, the story, graphics, controls, animations, everything. If you like story-based games or just like the idea of Assassin's Order, at least give this game a try. It really deserves your attention. Vittoria agli Assassini!", "hours": 62.5, "username": "Silencer", "products": 161, "early_access": false}
