{"product_id": "201870", "page": 129, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-10-06", "text": "AC2 started off with a very good storyline, which Brotherhood extended. However Revelations is where things got really interesting with the introduction of a variety of bombs which made completing missions a lot more \"have it your way\". Of all the AC2 titles, would definitely recommend Revelations the highest in terms of gameplay... although the original AC2 had a much more interesting storyline. Brotherhood was in-between the two on all counts!", "hours": 32.3, "username": "Potterified", "products": 834, "early_access": false}
