{"product_id": "201870", "page": 134, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-08-03", "text": "This is the last of Ezio saga.\nThe game involves more of Altair's last moment and more to the apple of eden.\nThe game is still fun to play but it's pretty much the same game as previous games. Unlike botherhood, it introduce the assassin dens. For this it's the same but you take over the territory. The fight, climb and everything else is pretty much the same thing.\nI would recommend for those fans but don't expect anything new about this. Apart from that, I have to say revelation isn't as great as previous titles though. I won't say much about the story, it more to finale to Ezio and Altair's story.\nMy Rating:\nExcellent\nGreat\nAverage\nBad\nGraphics: Excellent\nSound & music: Excellent\nGameplay: Great\nStory: Great", "hours": 44.5, "username": "NShade", "products": 132, "early_access": false}
