{"product_id": "201870", "page": 141, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-15", "text": "Assassin's Creed is one of the better games in the franchise,\ngraphical not a lot worse then Black Flag. The game also has a great storyline,\nand, a lot of fun to play, even without playing a story mission.\nRoaming through the streets of Instanbul is awesome,\nit's not a boring open world, a thing which would have made ACIII suck less.\nYou can spend a few hours on making the city free of Templars,\nand even more in the huge assassins-management minigame.\nA lot of bang for buck, mostly now it's older.\nThough you may think the multiplayer is impossible to play, because there are just a few people,\nyou can play multiplayer matches sometimes (not at 1 in the morning though).\nBut the coolest thing in the game is, of course, Ezio's SUPER AWESOME ACCENT!!", "hours": 136.1, "username": "Cerberus_", "products": 115, "early_access": false}
