{"product_id": "201870", "page": 142, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-05-31", "text": "This game is good, it really is, but as with all Assassin's Creed games, there's a lack of save or reasonable checkpoints and some BS storyline about a magical McGuffin, but I like the core mechanics, other than the stealth, If you let yourself, you'll lose yourself in the experience.", "hours": 25.7, "user_id": "76561198081941860", "username": "skeleponx", "products": 69, "early_access": false}
