{"product_id": "201870", "page": 144, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-05-02", "text": "Oh Another Assassin's Creed Game! Well this one is pretty darn good. You play as an aged Ezio, in the Byzantine/Ottoman controlled Copenhagen. Honestly the game's storyline could be a bit better, but improvements to the combat system, really smoothed the whole game over. Also the additons of \"Dens\" and more to do with your fellow assassins really was cool.", "hours": 31.2, "username": "Clay", "products": 477, "early_access": false}
