{"product_id": "201870", "page": 150, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-24", "text": "Assassins Creed Revelations is by far a great sequel in the Ezio trilogy, getting more in depth and letting the player realy connect with Ezio as he has gotten so much more older since he was in Assassins Creed 2, the player in this game must continue Ezio's story and see the end of Ezio and Altair as they both and Desmond clash together in this amazing story line. Great graphics and such a deep story and characters make this a game any gamer should have to complete the Ezio trilogy and the Assassins Creed Series! Highly recomened!", "hours": 0.7, "user_id": "76561198033981064", "username": "spartan-2694", "products": 27, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "201870", "page": 150, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-23", "text": "This game is awesome", "hours": 21.2, "user_id": "76561198053925484", "username": "D3bood", "products": 57, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "201870", "page": 150, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-23", "text": "When a man has won all his battles and defeated his enemies; what is left for him to achieve? Ezio Auditore must leave his life behind in search of answers, In search of the truth.\nIn Assassin\u2019s Creed\u00ae Revelations, master assassin Ezio Auditore walks in the footsteps of the legendary mentor Altair, on a journey of discovery and revelation. It is a perilous path \u2013 one that will take Ezio to Constantinople, the heart of the Ottoman Empire, where a growing army of Templars threatens to destabilize the region.\nIn addition to Ezio\u2019s award-winning story, a refined and expanded online multiplayer experience returns with more modes, more maps and more characters, allowing you to test your assassin skills against others from around the world.", "hours": 408.4, "username": "Tuong", "products": 2374, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "201870", "page": 150, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-23", "text": "Really cool game and if you're looking for a game for a good story i say pick this up and it has great combat!!!", "hours": 1.4, "user_id": "76561198086950392", "username": "OPTIC MICROWAVE SENPAI", "products": 58, "early_access": false}
