{"product_id": "201870", "page": 151, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-17", "text": "seems lacking for an assassin's creed game. still pretty fun, but doesn't quite live up to expectations. no riding horses, no outside of the animus sequences, and a generally smaller feeling than the previous two games. i think the lost archives dlc is the only one i actually played since i didn't do multiplayer, and it's not much fun though it does give some interesting glimpses into the story.", "hours": 28.6, "username": "misterhaan", "products": 2126, "early_access": false}
