{"product_id": "201870", "page": 152, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-12", "text": "Everyone complained that this game was medicore but really the only mediocre bits are the fact you have to keep reclaiming back territory you captured. Which I suppose is neat, but it's more frustrating than anything else really.", "hours": 26.4, "username": "Gvaz", "products": 1206, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "201870", "page": 152, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-12", "text": "First i have to say this game is for everyone that played all other AC's before!\nIf you did that then \"Revelations\" is just a glorious end of Ezio & Altair's story...!!\nThe storytelling is just one of the best i ever saw in a video game.. the game mechanics got polished and the graphics feel even nicer then before, and the city has definatly its charme...\nImho one of the best game stories ever ! Get them all if you can and start them in the correct order!\nThumbs Up!", "hours": 20.8, "username": "Chief_Jawa", "products": 304, "early_access": false}
