{"product_id": "201870", "page": 159, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-27", "text": "It has a good story line, and closes the chapter involving Ezio (which I think is a shame, since it doesn't show what happened to the rest of the family), it was kind of short though compared to brotherhood.\nOnly thing I had an issue with, the controls, they were so well laid out on the last game, in this one everything was configured in an odd manner for a keyboard and mouse layout, I had to reconfigure everything, to match the last game, and there were still a few controls that used to cover a couple of actions, that were separated for some reason.  If I had a 360 controller it wouldn't be a problem.", "hours": 35.9, "user_id": "76561197970160339", "username": "greds04", "products": 129, "early_access": false}
