{"product_id": "201870", "page": 167, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-09-13", "text": "My personal No. One in Assassin's Creed franchise. And even if any of its components isn't best comparing to others parts of this saga, Revelations is most  solid game about Desmond & friends. And only one I didn't get bored with before reaching credits.", "hours": 17.7, "username": "bogus", "products": 1173, "early_access": false}
