{"product_id": "201870", "page": 178, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-11-09", "text": "Another masterpiece in the series. To truly understand it, it's best to have played the previous games (in order of course), but even with out the background story, this game is a blast, and really leaves excitement for the next game in the series.", "hours": 16.1, "username": "AmericanBill", "products": 130, "early_access": false}
