{"product_id": "201870", "page": 197, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-12-27", "text": "Normally I try to be a completionist for the Assassin's Creed games but I decided not to this time. This game is pretty much like the last two in the series except a different location and even further improvements, it also furthers the storylyine, and believe me, the 18 plots that are going on at once are all getting REALLY good.", "hours": 13.0, "username": "ItadakiTom", "products": 491, "early_access": false}
