{"product_id": "201870", "page": 199, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-12-27", "text": "Yet another great addition to the Assasin's Creed series, though I find it to be a bit lacking compared to Brotherhood.", "hours": 43.4, "username": "Speedy", "products": 1708, "early_access": false}
