{"product_id": "201870", "page": 200, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-12-11", "text": "I know this isn't a popular opinion, but this remains my second-favorite game in the series (as of this writing, I haven't yet played Black Flag). The way it intertwines the stories of the three characters of the series is very cool. Though the bomb-crafting mechanic is a tad useless, it still makes for some fun moments.\nSCORE: 9.25/10", "hours": 32.9, "username": "StonedMagician", "products": 506, "early_access": false}
